statement.p:
Assuming the board is deflected by 6 inches,
and using typical materials and dimensions,
this equation simplifies to:

  W = W(L) \amp= \frac{(3)(6)(10{,}010{,}000)(1.64)}{L^3}
  \amp= \frac{295{,}495{,}200}{L^3}

